If you would like to contribute to this project, it is necessary to know the following:
1. Everything you contribute must abide by this document (CONTRIBUTING)
2. Features are submitted via PR's through docs/FEATURES with your attached feature
3. Code changes are allowed, however it is unlikely for me to check over a very big PR consisting of many changes.

Mostly accepted features and contributions towards the project:
1. Code reorganization
2. Common Optimizations
3. Library Updates
4. GUI Components corrections

Rarely accepted corrections:
1. Documentation alterations
2. License alterations
3. Source Files or Directories marked as permanent

Never accepted changes:
1. Major alteration towards GUI component ordering and placement
2. Library replacement
3. Unclear code refactoring

